videos.description: Ole Miss guard Cullen Neal drives to the basket looking for a layup, but is blocked by Tennessee forward Admiral Schofield. However, the blocked shot ricochets off the backboard and Rebels forward Marcanvis Hymon rises up for a putback dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (When a blocked shot turns into a dunk) 2017/01/17

videos.headline: When a blocked shot turns into a dunk

videos.description: Ole Miss senior guard Rasheed Brooks collapsed during a timeout in Tuesday's game against Tennessee. Brooks was taken to the hospital after suffering a seizure and is listed in stable condition.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB News (Ole Miss' Brooks collapses, taken to hospital) 2017/01/17
